WEBVTT

00:01:59.363 --> 00:02:00.521
where we live.

00:02:00.545 --> 00:02:02.092
The world was changing.

00:02:02.116 --> 00:02:05.093
It was about to change
in ways that nobody could foresee.

00:02:05.117 --> 00:02:08.775
A few weeks later, Woodstock happened.

00:02:09.385 --> 00:02:11.465
Three days of fun and music.

00:02:11.489 --> 00:02:13.589
Here, just for historical authenticity,

00:02:13.613 --> 00:02:15.412
is a picture of me in that year.

00:02:15.436 --> 00:02:18.662
(Laughter)

00:02:18.686 --> 00:02:20.663
Yeah, the wavy hair, the blue eyes --

00:02:20.687 --> 00:02:21.900
it was really something.

00:02:22.350 --> 00:02:24.327
That fall of 1969,

00:02:24.351 --> 00:02:26.238
the Whole Earth Catalog came out.

00:02:26.262 --> 00:02:29.726
It was a hippie journal
of self-sufficiency.

00:02:29.750 --> 00:02:32.781
We think of hippies
of being just hedonists,